metadata.name: Azurite
metadata.description:
The deep sea opens its gates, an emergence approaches. Dive into a world free of limitations. 

 Six thousand towers from Alma x Jack Irving. 

 Six individual towers emerge from the depths. 

 Collect all six to be rewarded. 

 Follow [AlmaXJackIrving](https://twitter.com/almaXjackirving) to discover future utility.
